divs: sighting detailsat around 2am my dog needed to go out. i went out to the fenced off back yard and was admiring the beautiful orange red "full moon" in back of my house i saw through the trees. i realized at this time the moon should be over my house. when i turned around there was the moon and when i turned back the orange\red "full moon" was gone. i noticed three head lights below tree top level coming through the woods at me about 200? feet away. the vehicle looked the size of a vw bug but was black and rectangular about four feet high? and 10 feet long? i was scared and ran inside to wake my then husband. he would not wake up. i looked outside standing on our deck but saw nothing.
Summary: Black rectangular Vehicle with three headlights
